Grimlock overheard the bums words. He snorted in that direction. He
turned to his Dinobots. "Autobots not know what they getting into." He
flexed his arm. "Dinobots do. We survive. There no room for weak, come,
we board." He said, as he walked towards the shuttle. He had no
possesions on Cybertron he needed.

Hoist drove up, and transformed. "Well, i'm ready to see earth again."
He said cheerfully.
